Overview
The Email Notification System is a production-ready, enterprise-grade email service designed for high availability, scalability and reliability. It provides synchronous and asynchronous email delivery with comprehensive error handling, retry mechanisms and monitoring capabilities.

CF1-2817: enable notifications to researchers for rejected sources
Requirements Completed
 

Key Features
✅ Synchronous and asynchronous email sending

✅ HTML and plain text email support

✅ CC/BCC support with validation

✅ File attachments with size limits

✅ Custom metadata support

✅ Retry mechanism with exponential backoff

✅ Circuit breaker pattern for fault tolerance

✅ Comprehensive error handling and logging

✅ Email validation and sanitization

✅ Dead letter queue for failed messages

